elements.name: TC_016 Account must be confirmed via email

steps.name: User go to minuteEmail to receive a valid email
User receive the email from the page they go to
The user returns to the hub-comfy page and enters the email in the email box
User clicks the RE-SEND CODE button
The user goes back to minuteEmail to get the code sent to the email address
User receives the code and returns to hubcomfy
The user enters the code that comes to the e-mail address entered in the Verification Code box
The user enters the same valid password in the confirm password as they enter in the password
The user verifies seeing the text Welcome to Hubcomfy!
The user goes to minuteEmail to verify incoming email
The user clicks on the Hubcomfy email
